msg: Addition of a kernel builder utility that provides support for the handling of property file inspection for a merlin.implemetation property that can be used to switch in alternative implementation of the kernel based on client property settings.

msg: Add generic support for the location of a current implementation artifact specification using a supplied properties filename and key.
